        {
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "I forgot that number isn't set by default.\r\n\r\nSo options:\r\n\r\n1. Do nothing\r\n2. Change anyway and rely only on text highlights if user hasn't enabled numbers\r\n3. Set default signs based on `signcolumn` and `number` values\r\n4. Change `number` default too\r\n\r\nI'd be for either 1 or 3, with slight preference for 3. But overall no strong opinion on this at all.\r\n",
            "created_at": "2026-03-23T15:21:23Z",
            "html_url": "https://github.com/neovim/neovim/pull/38441#issuecomment-4111456765",
            "id": 4111456765,
            "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/neovim/neovim/issues/38441",
