            }
        },
        {
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "> Most users enable one or both of those options anyway.\r\n\r\n[Citation needed]\r\n\r\nNo, sorry, I really don't think that's an acceptable remedy. The jumping is annoying, but just not showing signs at all is throwing the baby out with the bathwater.\r\n\r\nEither we make this conditional (complicating the default logic significantly) or \"debounce\" hiding the signcolumn somehow.",
